                                                                                              SA-08(24)       SECURITY AND PRIVACY ENGINEERING PRINCIPLES | SECURE FAILURE AND RECOVERY
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SA-08(24)_ODP[01]     systems or system components that implement the security design principle of
                                                                                                                                    secure failure are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-08(24)_ODP[02]     systems or system components that implement the security design principle of
                                                                                                                                    secure recovery are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              SA-08(24)[01]         <SA-08(24)_ODP[01] systems or system components> implement the security
                                                                                                                                    design principle of secure failure;

                                                                                                              SA-08(24)[02]         <SA-08(24)_ODP[02] systems or system components> implement the security
                                                                                                                                    design principle of secure recovery.

